race.comment: WILL VANSON (1) finished well back at this track last time when a 4 length sixth (16.75) but scored four back at this track (19.30). Solid record here at the distance winning five races. Can discover winning form. STOJANOVIC (8) made it two minor placings on the trot when beaten third (16.79) in a Grade 5 at this track last time out. Well placed here and can atone this time. HALF MAC (7) could manage only third last time but ran a handy time (16.80) in a hot race. Worth including.
